name: SFS L-s9.3 Laser Cannons
Lore: 'Developed by Sienar Fleet Systems weapons division to provide added firepower against shielded Rebel fighters. Also provides added coverage to increase accuracy.',
Text: 'Deploy on your TIE Avenger, TIE Interceptor or TIE Defender. May target a starfighter using X Force, where X = 0 to 3. Draw destiny. If destiny + X > defense value, target hit (lost instead if X = 3).',
